OL,3,CGrieving mums say new NHS safety rule
OL,4,Cis a start but 'does not go far enough'
OL,6,FZoe Muldoon spoke to Julie and Melanie
OL,7,Fabout Martha's Rule and the why they
OL,8,Ffeel they were let down by medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals
OL,11,FTwo mothers who both lost their sons
OL,12,Fafter being turned away from hospitals
OL,13,Fhave welcomed a new scheme that gives
OL,14,Fpatients the right to a second
OL,15,Fopinion, but warned it does not go far
OL,16,Fenough.
OL,18,FMothers Julie Alfrey and Melanie
OL,19,FTheophine have been campaigning since
OL,20,Ftheir sons died days after they were
OL,21,Fdischarged from hospital.
