OL,6,FJulie's son, Johnny Alfrey, died of
OL,7,Fmulti-organ failure caused by acute
OL,8,Fcardiac failure on 24 June 2022 at the
OL,9,Fage of 22.
OL,11,FHis mother Julie said: "He had this
OL,12,Fbigger picture of how he wanted this
OL,13,Fworld to be; peaceful and kind. He
OL,14,Fwanted everyone to be happy and he
OL,15,Fmade everyone happy."
OL,17,FDescribed by his parents as "a perfect
OL,18,Fson", Johnny was a passionate musician
OL,19,Ffrom and student at the . However, his
OL,20,Flife was cut short days after he was
OL,21,Fdischarged from Fairfield Hospital in .
