OL,6,F"They wouldn't let us look at the
OL,7,Fnotes, which we asked for several
OL,8,Ftimes, and after the fact we found
OL,9,Fthere were lots of mistakes written in
OL,10,Fthe notes and none of our opinions
OL,11,Fwere written in the notes."
OL,13,FAn investigation carried out by the
OL,14,FNorthern Care Alliance NHS Foundation
OL,15,FTrust, which runs Fairfield Hospital,
OL,16,Fdetermined a series of failures that
OL,17,Fcontributed towards Johnny's death.
