OL,6,FIt's a similar story for Melanie,
OL,7,Fwho's son, James Theophine from , died
OL,8,Fat the age of 20 from organ failure
OL,9,Fthree days after he was discharged
OL,10,Ffrom hospital.
OL,12,FMelanie said: "He was really turning
OL,13,Finto a lovely young man, and I was
OL,14,Flooking forward to the man he was
OL,15,Fgoing to become.
