OL,6,F"I just didn't see how somebody could
OL,7,Fbe so healthy one minute, and dead the
OL,8,Fnext. I really didn't understand it,
OL,9,Fand I thought something's gone wrong,
OL,10,Fthis isn't right. Something's been
OL,11,Fmissed."
OL,13,FBoth mothers have been campaigning
OL,14,Fsince the death of their sons for
OL,15,Fpatients to have the right to see
OL,16,Ftheir own medical notes and request a
OL,17,Fsecond opinion.
