OL,4,Cis a start but 'does not go far enough'
OL,6,FMelanie said: "I could have asked for
OL,7,Fa second opinion then, and spoke to
OL,8,Fthe person with the notes they had so
OL,9,Ffar, I don't think he would have been
OL,10,Fdischarged."
OL,12,FIn April 2024, 100 NHS trusts across
OL,13,FEngland will roll out Martha's Rule.
OL,14,FThe scheme is named after Martha
OL,15,FMills, who died from sepsis after a
OL,16,Fwrong hospital diagnosis.
